fields.content: Today, I had my calculus midterm and found it very tough. I feel bad that I did not study hard enough for it. I wish I did not have back-to-back midterms.
My chemistry midterm today was even worse than my calculus midterm yesterday. I feel horrible and just want this week to be over.
It's finally the weekend and my friends cheered me up and made me forget about the past midterms. I'm grateful for having such close friends!

I'm going to try my best to finish working on the assignment due tomorrow. I've struggled with keeping up with the workload this term but I feel like that working in groups will get me through the term.
I've handed in my assignment and felt great that I got it done. But, today was also the day we got back our physics midterm and I borderline passed.
